#!/usr/bin/env escript
-module(main).
-export([main/1]).

% Generated by Mochi transpiler v0.10.35 (84642adc7) on 2025-07-22 11:10 +0700

main(_) ->
    People = [#{"age" => 30, "email" => "alice@example.com", "name" => "Alice"}, #{"age" => 15, "email" => "bob@example.com", "name" => "Bob"}, #{"age" => 20, "email" => "charlie@example.com", "name" => "Charlie"}],
    Adults = [#{"name" => maps:get("name", P), "email" => maps:get("email", P)} ||
        P <- People,
        (maps:get("age", P) >= 18)],
    lists:foreach(fun(A) ->
    io:format("~p ~p~n", [maps:get("name", A), maps:get("email", A)])
end, Adults).
